624
00:51:34,520 --> 00:51:36,397
Oh, officer!

625
00:51:37,360 --> 00:51:38,713
- Hello.
- Hi.

626
00:51:38,800 --> 00:51:42,190
- He's hoping to go to university too.
- Oh, where to?

627
00:51:42,280 --> 00:51:45,192
Maybe Nottingham, to read English.

628
00:51:45,280 --> 00:51:48,590
